    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... the \"working with it\" part is what's killing me. it's just constant effort for zero reward. it feels like trying to rebuild a house that's already burned down to ash. maybe some things just aren't meant to be rebuilt. maybe it's just easier to just... stop fighting it. don't you think it's exhausting to keep trying to fix something that's just fundamentally gone?",
